                    '})|raw}}
                </div>
                <div class="col  col--third">
                    {{widget('image', 'home--about-image2', {
                      'src': asset('/images/icon--people.png')
                    })|raw}}
                    {{widget('content', 'home--about-text3', { content:'
                        <h2>Strong Relationships</h2>
                        <p>FDM have a strong relationship with 100s of enterprise level SMB services providers. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur elim sed do eiusmod tempor.</p>
